            <abstract>
                <p>Magic prayer against the evil eye with an invocation of the Cross. 
                    The word <foreign xml:lang="gez">manso</foreign> in the incipit might be related to 
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">mansawa</foreign> "lead to temptation" or to <foreign xml:lang="gez">manšo</foreign>, which is 
                    described by <bibl><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1972Wellcome"/><citedRange unit="page"></citedRange>49</bibl> as 
                    "a disease which recurs attacking the same person, like intermittent fever, rheumatism, migraine, etc.".</p>
